        <abstract> 
<p>Italian translation [of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] is delayed, but printing should begin soon.</p>  
<p>Will send CD one of his writings in which he defends the natural descent of man [<hi rend="italic">Origin dell’uomo</hi>, 2d ed. (1870)].</p> 
            <p>CD’s theory is making great progress in Italy and daily gains supporters.</p>
        </abstract>
